    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8012141/" class="title-link">浅析章学诚“新史学”的理论基础及其意图</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8012141"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
